          Health and wellness products that support your journey to optimal living.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center text-amber-600 text-sm font-medium">
          <span>Explore Collection</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      
      <!-- Category 4 -->
      <a href="/collections/exclusive-tech" class="category-card group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-amber-300">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Exclusive Tech</h3>
